# No environment variables required for basic deployment.
# The app runs entirely on Cloudflare Workers Free tier with no secrets.

# OPTIONAL: If you want to restrict the CORS proxy to specific origins,
# set this to a comma-separated list of allowed origins:
# ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://yourdomain.com,https://xan.example.com

# OPTIONAL: If you want to change the AllAnime API endpoint:
# ALLANIME_API=https://api.allanime.day/api

# NOTE: All settings (theme, autoplay, volume, etc.) are stored in
# the user's browser localStorage — no server-side env vars needed.
